- structure aliases listed below, where:
- - Array index starts with 0:
- - - f(x,y)=x*y  ;has [x} as its [0th parameter] and [y] as its [1th parameter]
- - - A formulaOne race car has 0 drivers and 3 tires
- - - The fastest racer of a race always achieves 0th place of a race
- - - 2-dimensional spacetime (minkovski diagram) has 0 time domains and 2 space domains
- - - the length of an array is equal to the position of its last entry

v*   = linear matrix = vector  with [*]         fields
m*   = square matrix           with [*]-squared fields
d*** = single variate calculus over [*] domains down to [tally of *] derivatives
C*** = multivatiate   calculus over [*] domains down to [tally of *] derivatives
[tally of *] == [stick counting], in a base1System
- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unary_numeral_system
- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Repdigit

*/
